{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1699-06_009","@resp":"wordpro","head":{"value":"[Ode qui a remporté le Prix de l'Academie des Jeux Floraux]","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", juin 1699 [tome 6], p. 9-15.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"value":"Rien n’estant plus propre à animer ceux qui ont du talent pour l’Eloquence &amp; pour la Poësie, que les prix que l’on distribuë sur les sujets que les Académies proposent, il ne faut pas s’étonner si l’on travaille à l’envy pour les remporter. Le Pere Lami, Prestre de la Doctrine Chrestienne, &amp; Professeur de Rhétorique au College de Toulouse, a eu cette année le plus considerable de l’Académie des Jeux Floraux. Il avoit remporté l’année précedente celuy de l’Académie des Lanternistes. C’est un homme d’un merite distingué, &amp; qui s’est acquis l’estime de tous ceux qui le connoissent. Voicy son dernier Ouvrage.","id":"/div/p"},"quote":{"#":[{"label":{"#":[{"#":{"value":"A LA LOUANGE","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#[0]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"de la Poësie.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#[2]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"ODE.","id":"/div/quote/#[0]/label/#[4]/#"}}]}},{"lg":{"l":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quel feu, quels transports, quelle audace,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[0]/hi/#"}}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Saisissent mes sens &amp; mon cœur,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et quel Dieu sur un char vainqueur","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"M’éleve au sommet du Parnasse !","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Déja le beau son de ma voix","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Charme les échos de ces bois,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Où Malherbe encor nous enchante.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pour m’en découvrir les détours,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"O Muses, qu’en mes vers je chante,","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Venez toutes à mon secours.","id":"/div/quote/#[1]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Delicieuse frenesie,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Noble amusement des esprits,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Beauté dont les cœurs sont épris,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Incomparable Poësie,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tes ailes peuvent tout oser :","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"C’est au Ciel que tu vas puiser","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La rapidité de tes flâmes.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que ton art est ingenieux :","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Il meut, il transporte les ames,","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et des hommes il fait des Dieux.","id":"/div/quote/#[3]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[4]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Jadis les rochers se fendirent","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Touchez par de tendres regrets.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"On vit les monts &amp; les forests","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Suivre la voix qu’ils entendirent.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Les pierres dans le mouvement","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vont se placer artistement","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Au gré du son qui les attire :","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tous ces spectacles plus qu’humain ;","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Font voir ce que peut une Lyre","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’animent de sçavantes mains.","id":"/div/quote/#[5]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[6]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tes traits, aussi puissans qu’aimables,","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ouvrent un passage aux amours","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"En des lieux qui furent toûjours","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Au Soleil même impenetrables.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Tes accens vifs &amp; douloureux","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Percent le séjour tenebreux","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De l’inaccessible Tenare ;","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ta voix y réveille les morts ;","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Cet empire dur &amp; barbare","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Devient sensible à tes accords.","id":"/div/quote/#[7]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[8]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Parcourons les Champs Elisées.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Où suis-je ! Quel est mon effroy !","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ah ! quels grands hommes j’entrevoy !","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qu’icy leurs ombres sont prisées !","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Homere, le Dieu des Auteurs,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Pindare, &amp; ses imitateurs,","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Y brillent par leurs harmonies ;","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et parmi ces divinitez","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Se mêlent ces fameux genies","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que l’Orne &amp; la Seine ont portez.","id":"/div/quote/#[9]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[10]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" On vante ces ames hautaines,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui bravant l’horreur du trépas","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Alloient aux plus lointains climats","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Arborer les Aigles Romaines.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que de siecles ont applaudi","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"A ce Heros jeune &amp; hardi,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Qui de tant de Rois eut l’hommage !","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Mais ces Vainqueurs de l’Univers","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Eclatent moins par leur courage,","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Que par la puissance des vers.","id":"/div/quote/#[11]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[12]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Malgré les fieres destinées,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ces grands noms exempts du cercueil","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Surmonteront avec orgueil","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"La longue suite des années.","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Muses, quel triomphe pour vous !","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Un Roy, qui les efface tous,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et vous cultive, &amp; vous honore ;","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous charmez ses soins éclatans,","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Lors qu’il est tout poudreux encore","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De la défaite des Titans.","id":"/div/quote/#[13]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[14]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Chantez ses grandes avantures,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Chantez ses immenses bienfaits,","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et du torrent de ses hauts-faits","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Inondez les races futures.","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"L’éclat de tant d’exploits guerriers","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Rendra plus brillans les Lauriers","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Dont vôtre teste est embelie.","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Jamais l’étonnante grandeur","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[7]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"De la Grece &amp; de l’Italie","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Ne vous combla de tant d’honneur.","id":"/div/quote/#[15]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote/#[16]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" Quel siecle offrit une matiere","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Plus digne du sacré Valon ?","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Est-il pour les sœurs d’Appollon","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[2]/hi/#"}}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Une plus illustre carriere ?","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[3]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Quoy ! faibles Muses, vous tremblez !","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[4]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Non : Que vos efforts redoublez","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[5]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Consacrent son heureuse histoire,","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[6]/#"}},{"hi":[{"@rend":"sc","#":{"value":"Louis","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[7]/hi[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"sçaura vous soûtenir ;","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[7]/hi[1]/#"}}]},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Et du seul récit de sa gloire","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[8]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vous surprendrez tout l’avenir.","id":"/div/quote/#[17]/lg/l[9]/#"}}]}}]}}}